<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3534792>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Trigonostomum sinensis n. sp: (A) live specimen; (B) squeezed live specimen; (C–F) reproductive organs (partim); (G–H) bursal appendage; (I–J) copulatory organ." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3534792/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3534796>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Trigonostomum sinensis n. sp: (A) habitus from a live animal; (B) sagittal reconstruction of atrial organs, showing reproductive organs (partim); (C) copulatory organ; (D) stylet; (E) plate I; (F) plate II; (G) bursal appendage." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3534796/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3534794>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Trigonostomum sinensis n. sp: (A) whole mount; (B–C) whole mount, showing the reproductive organs (partim); (D–H) serially-sectioned (sagittal) specimens." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3534794/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

